result.name: Mutation Analysis of CDH1 gene in Canine Breast Tumors
result.description: A study on mutation analysis of CDH1 gene implicated in canine mammary tumors through Sanger Sequencing. 20 mammary tumor and non-tumorous samples of female dog were analyzed during this research.
result.center: Institute of Biochemistry and Biotechnology, University of Veterinary & Animal Sciences, Pakistan
